cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software in academic or other published work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "Firefox LLM Bridge"
abstract: >-
  An open-source AI browser agent for Mozilla Firefox, distributed as a
  Manifest V3 WebExtension. Connects Firefox to local (Ollama) or cloud
  (Anthropic Claude, OpenAI GPT, Google Gemini) LLMs and enables them to
  read, navigate, and act on web pages through a semantic accessibility map.
